=>Mostly used for plotting continuous data.
=>Used for identifying trends in data.

Now we will use the same method of plotting chart by Firstly selecting the whole excel data next goto  insert menu and click on recommended charts.

We can also see different chart layout by going on insert menu and click on  Quick Layout and select line chart layout
and if we have a doubt about the data being plotted in the chart we can confirm it by clicking on select data
and seeing it accordingly.

Now we will change chart type by going inside design menu and clicking in change chart type.
In any case mostly use 2D line chart as 3D line chart will not give us proper value in any case.
